docs.abstract: Survey findings are prompting the profession’s leaders to take action to prevent sex discrimination and physical abuse of female economists.
docs.snippet: Survey findings are prompting the profession’s leaders to take action to prevent sex discrimination and physical abuse of female economists.
docs.lead_paragraph: Nearly 100 female economists say a peer or a colleague has sexually assaulted them. Nearly 200 say they were the victim of an attempted assault. And hundreds say they were stalked or touched inappropriately, according to a far-reaching survey of the field.

headline.main: Women in Economics Report Rampant Sexual Assault and Bias
headline.print_headline: Women Face High Levels Of Sex Abuse In Economics

docs.abstract: When an inveterate tweeter and social media hound decided to change his ways, what did he turn to? An email newsletter.
docs.snippet: When an inveterate tweeter and social media hound decided to change his ways, what did he turn to? An email newsletter.
docs.lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO — My favorite new social network doesn’t incessantly spam me with notifications. When I post, I’m not bombarded with @mentions from bots and trolls. And after I use it, I don’t worry about ads following me around the web.

headline.main: The New Social Network That Isn’t New at All
